front.title: IEEE Standards for Local and Metropolitan Area Networks: Supplement to Integrated Services (IS) LAN Interface at the Medium Access Control (MAC) and Physical (PHY) Layers: Protocol Implementation Conformance Statement (PICS) Proforma
front.abstract: Administratively withdrawn. The Protocol Implementation Conformance Statement (PICS) proforma for IEEE Std 802.9-1994 is provided. It does not include the Managed Objects Conformance Statement, which is contained in a separate supplement.
